<i>Mutant apprehension</i>
<i>in progress.</i>

20:21.887 --> 20:25.123
<i>Mutant apprehension</i>
<i>in progress.</i>

20:25.125 --> 20:29.595
Charles, how does it
come to this?

20:29.597 --> 20:33.398
Because of the X-Men.
What are you saying?

20:33.400 --> 20:36.069
Each of you will admit
defeat and walk away.

20:36.071 --> 20:38.638
Only as team
do you stand a chance.

20:38.640 --> 20:40.039
Only together

20:40.041 --> 20:42.342
can you change
the course of the future.

20:42.344 --> 20:45.278
And you, Logan--
You must lead them.

20:46.748 --> 20:49.484
I don't know, Charles.

20:49.486 --> 20:51.153
