a good fit.

20:51.155 --> 20:52.220
Make it fit, Logan.

20:52.222 --> 20:56.325
Otherwise all is lost.

20:56.327 --> 20:59.261
Scott, do not abandon
the team.

20:59.263 --> 21:02.065
We cannot win this
without you, son.

21:04.569 --> 21:06.003
I must go,

21:06.005 --> 21:08.638
but I will try
and make contact again.

21:15.781 --> 21:18.016
