21:57.963 --> 22:00.933
Whatever's eating away at us,
we get past it.

22:00.935 --> 22:04.569
We rise to the occasion
because we're a team

22:04.571 --> 22:07.240
and we've got a job to do.

22:10.844 --> 22:13.814
The world needs
the X-Men.

